description:
This Pilot Pack is included in the Starlink: Battle for Atlas™ Collection 1 Pack. Check it out for the best way to complete your fleet!*

Levi McCray is a West Coast daredevil, extreme sports athlete, and internet star. He has no boundaries and always has to be the center of attention.

* Starlink: Battle For Atlas game required to play. This pack includes one digital Levi McCray Pilot.*

*Starlink: Battle For Atlas™ game required to play. Rush into danger, counting on luck and quick thinking to make it through with Levi's unique Pilot Ability, Danger Zone.* *This pack is included in the Digital and Deluxe Editions of Starlink: Battle for Atlas™.
name: Starlink: Battle for Atlas™ Digital Levi McCray Pilot Pack
